data.description: Incredible 3 bedroom, 2 bath completely updated home only 100 ft from Lake Conroe in the highly sought after golf-course community of April Sound. Inside boasts an open layout with the kitchen open to the dining and living room, a perfect space for entertaining. Upgrades include granite counters, beautiful LVP flooring, stainless steel appliances and subway tile backsplash. The master suite is light and bright with an ensuite featuring floor to ceiling walk-in tile shower and large walk-in closet. Both guest suites are generous in size with elevated ceilings and ceiling fans. The oversize front covered patio is an excellent space for morning coffee or evening dinners. April Sound is conveniently located off 105 in Conroe, Texas. The 24 hour manned gate community amenities include 3 different 9-hole golf courses, April Sound Marina with community boat launch, parks, pools, tennis courts and is golfcart friendly. Short term rentals allowed! Make this your next home or investment today!
